%% Reprice Negotiation Flow — One-Shot Price Negotiation within RFP Workflow
%% ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant UI_C as QuoteComparison.tsx
    participant DB as Firestore
    participant UI_V as VendorQuoteResponse.tsx
    participant V as Vendor

    Note over C, V: Normal RFP flow: Vendor submits quote → Customer reviews

    C->>UI_C: Clicks "Request New Price"
    UI_C->>UI_C: Opens modal (proposed price + reason)
    C->>UI_C: Enters $X.XX + optional reason
    UI_C->>DB: requestReprice(responseId, priceCents, reason)
    DB-->>DB: Set repriceStatus='requested', start 24h timer
    UI_C->>V: 🔔 notifyVendorRepriceRequested (bell + email/SMS/push)
    UI_C-->>C: Toast: "Reprice request sent!"
    UI_C-->>UI_C: Shows "Waiting for vendor — Xh Ym remaining"

    Note over V: Vendor has 24 hours to respond

    V->>UI_V: Sees amber "Price Negotiation Request" panel

    alt Vendor Accepts
        V->>UI_V: Clicks "Accept Price"
        UI_V->>DB: respondToReprice(id, 'accept')
        DB-->>DB: repriceStatus='vendor_accepted', total=requestedPrice
        UI_V->>C: 🔔 notifyCustomerRepriceResponse('accepted')
        Note over C: Customer sees green "Price accepted!" banner
        C->>UI_C: Can now Accept/Decline quote at new price
    else Vendor Denies
        V->>UI_V: Clicks "Decline"
        UI_V->>DB: respondToReprice(id, 'deny')
        DB-->>DB: repriceStatus='vendor_denied', total unchanged
        UI_V->>C: 🔔 notifyCustomerRepriceResponse('denied')
        Note over C: Customer sees yellow "Price declined" banner
        C->>UI_C: Can still Accept/Decline at original price
    else Vendor Counters
        V->>UI_V: Clicks "Counter-Offer" → enters $Y.YY + note
        UI_V->>DB: respondToReprice(id, 'counter', counterPrice)
        DB-->>DB: repriceStatus='vendor_countered', start 24h customer timer
        UI_V->>C: 🔔 notifyCustomerRepriceResponse('countered', counterPrice)

        Note over C: Customer has 24 hours to respond to counter

        alt Customer Accepts Counter
            C->>UI_C: Clicks "Accept Counter"
            UI_C->>DB: resolveCounterOffer(id, 'accept')
            DB-->>DB: repriceStatus='counter_accepted', total=counterPrice
            UI_C->>V: 🔔 notifyVendorCounterResolved(accepted=true)
            Note over C: Quote total updated to counter price
        else Customer Declines Counter
            C->>UI_C: Clicks "Decline"
            UI_C->>DB: resolveCounterOffer(id, 'decline')
            DB-->>DB: repriceStatus='counter_declined', total unchanged
            UI_C->>V: 🔔 notifyVendorCounterResolved(accepted=false)
            Note over C: Original price stands
        else Timer Expires
            DB-->>DB: expireStaleRepriceRequests() → repriceStatus='expired'
            Note over C, V: Counter-offer expired, original price stands
        end
    else Timer Expires (No Vendor Response)
        DB-->>DB: expireStaleRepriceRequests() → repriceStatus='expired'
        Note over C: Shows "Price negotiation expired" banner
    end

    Note over C, V: After resolution: Customer can Accept/Decline quote normally
    Note over C, V: ONE-SHOT: "Request New Price" button never shown again
